ActSpecies at Risk Act
PrecisORDER (a) GIVING NOTICE OF DECISIONS NOT TO ADD the five populations of beluga whale, the porbeagle shark and the Lower Fraser River and Middle Fraser River populations of white sturgeon to the List of Wildlife Species at Risk and to REFER THE ASSESSMENT done on the Verna's flower moth back to COSEWIC for further information and consideration; and (b) APPROVING THE STATEMENTS to be placed in the Public Registry setting out the reasons for the preceding decisions.
